head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths PITCHER, JANE DUNWOODY

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths PITCHER, JANE DUNWOODY

block.p: PITCHER--Jane Dunwoody, 92, of West Chester and Hatboro, PA, April 2, 2007. Widow of Col. Jack Griffin Pitcher. Survived by daughter, Barbara Pitcher. 11:30am-12:30pm on April 10th Hogan Funeral Home, 135 Main St., Highland Falls, NY 10928. 1:30 pm, Old Cadet Chapel, West Point, NY. Post Cemetery. Founds Funeral Home, West Chester.
